<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/103000844/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """Types of Evaluation
1. Continuous (Progressive) Evaluation
The evaluation of the students will be based on the characteristics of the elective course.
2. Global Evaluation
Depending on the characteristics of the elective course, the evaluation will consist of either a resubmission of the tests or a single test.
3. Extraordinary Evaluation
A single test"""@es ;
